---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="page-shell max-w-3xl border-[#2802fc] bg-[#9036c1]">
    <h1 class="page-title pb-4 text-white">-- About Me --</h1>
    <h2 class="pb-5 text-center font-display text-[16pt] text-white">
      Hello! You've reached Eising.net, the personal website of Shane Eising: Developer, Writer, and Musician!
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 p-1 text-left text-[14pt] text-white">
      <p>In addition to working as a Software Analyst full-time, I'm an aspiring musical theatre composer / lyricist / playwright, as well as a (technically commissioned) writer of murder-mystery dinners.</p>
      <p>I've also been known to write the occasional poem, and when distracted enough will compose music in other genres/forms/mediums (video game scoring, songwriting, and a one-off attempt at modern classical chamber music). Check out the Portfolio page for a taste of all that!</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
